 2. the old-henry-smoker is the old-henry-smoker##1
 3. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 4. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the havana-smoker is the thai##1
 6. the british is the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the british is between the bluemaster-smoker and the person driving the trike##2
 8. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the indian##1
 9. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
10. the colombian is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
11. the indian is on the right of the british##1
12. the person driving the bus is the canadian##1
13. the egyptian is on the left of the british##1
14. the egyptian is on the right of the person driving the train##1
15. the canadian is on the far right##1
16. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
