 4. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the van and the person eating pear##2
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person eating pear##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
10. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
11. the person driving the roller is the person eating grapes##1
12. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
14. the person driving the van is the person drinking water##1
15. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

