.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: zinnia, sunflower, daisy, balloon-flower, aconite, marigold, iris
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, house, metal, punk, reggae, salsa, trance
7 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, ferret, guinea-pig, hedgehog, mouse, snake
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 2. the owner of the mouse is between the fan of reggae and the fan of metal##2
 3. the fan of d&b is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 4. the fan of trance is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 5. the fan of d&b is the person who growszinnia##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is in the middle##1
 7. the person who growsaconite is the fan of salsa##1
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the fan of d&b is the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the person who growsiris is the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
12. the fan of trance is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
13. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
14. the fan of house is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
15. the person who growsiris is on the right of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Flower           | sunflower | marigold | aconite | daisy  | iris   | balloon-flower | zinnia      |
| Music-Genre   | trance | metal        | salsa    | reggae     | punk     | house   | d&b        |
| Pet           | bird   | ferret       | mouse    | guinea-pig | hedgehog | snake   | chinchilla |

