.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-17::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, cooking, dancing, gardening, hiking, photography, woodworking
7 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, hedgehog, lizard, rat, turtle
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, lemonade, cola, hot-chocolate, coffee, tea
 1. the person drinking tea is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is baking##2
 2. the person drinking tea is the owner of the frog##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 9. the owner of the dog is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
10. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the owner of the lizard##1
13. the person drinking cola is the owner of the rat##1
14. the person who's hobby is baking is the person drinking water##1
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Hobby       | dancing  | photography | gardening  | woodworking | cooking | hiking | baking |
| Pet         | hedgehog | goldfish    | dog        | lizard      | rat     | frog   | turtle |
| Beverage   | lemonade  | iced-tea   | hot-chocolate | coffee        | cola    | tea  | water   |

