.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-19::.
7 different games are played: domino, billiard, whist, mah-jongg, monopoly, bridge, canasta
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, crime, disaster, documentary, drama, satire, time-travel
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: golf, handball, ice-hockey, skiing, snowboarding, soccer, volleyball
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 4. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 5. the person playing bridge is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 6. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 7. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
11. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
12. the person who's sport is golf is between the person playing whist and the person who's sport is soccer##2
13. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
14. the person watching action movies is the person who's sport is soccer##1
15. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |      4      |      5       |      6      |      7       |
| Game           | whist      | domino | monopoly | billiard   | bridge | mah-jongg | canasta |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | disaster   | action   | documentary | crime        | drama       | satire       |
| Sport         | handball    | golf       | soccer   | skiing      | volleyball   | ice-hockey  | snowboarding |

